          "doc": "Exchange rate: fiat units per 1 USDC at 7-decimal precision.\\nTaken directly from the rates API, e.g. \"GBP\": \"13503230\".",
          "name": "rate",
          "type_": "i128"
        },
        {
          "doc": "Current USDC balance of reserve_address (hot wallet), 7 decimals.",
          "name": "reserve_balance",
          "type_": "i128"
        },
        {
          "doc": "Ed25519 signature over the canonical 56-byte message above.",
          "name": "signature",
          "type_": {
            "bytes_n": {
              "n": 64
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "doc": "Unix timestamp (seconds) \\xe2\\x80\\x94 last_update_unix from the rates API response.",
          "name": "timestamp",
          "type_": "u64"
        },
        {
          "doc": "Sum of all fiat tokens in circulation converted to USDC at current\\nrates, 7 decimals.  Pre-calculated by backend, tamper-proof because\\nit is covered by the Ed25519 signature.",
